    Title: Kinesiotape for Edema After Bilateral Total Knee Arthroplasty

    Trial Summary:
    Kinesio Tape, an elastic cotton strip with adhesive, is used to reduce swelling in the lower leg. It's applied in a specific pattern by a trained physical therapist, known as a Certified Kinesiotape Practitioner. This method is designed to provide support and aid in the management of leg swelling.

